               übernachten übermorgen <hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb987" type="place">Toblach</rs></hi> reisen – Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t <signed><hi rend="latintype">Arthur</hi></signed></p></div>
